    "This yields an approach that is more flexible than Prompt Tuning, which primarily operates at the input embedding level.",
    "• Prefix vectors are inserted as learnable parameters at each Transformer layer.",
    "• The main model parameters remain frozen.",
    "• Only the prefix vectors are optimized to align the model with downstream tasks.",
    "Benefits of Prefix Tuning: • More Expressive than Prompt Tuning: Because it modifies activations across multiple Transformer layers, Prefix Tuning can capture more complex adaptations, potentially leading to better performance on tasks that demand deeper model adjustments."
